column5: ~~~~Just got off the phone with the operator at Virgina Beach Marina, and he reports the bay is clear of ive and Sib's Ramp is clear also, can you guess where I'll be this Sat.
Where ta hell is Virgina Beach Marina !!!!!!!!!!!!!!   i 'll find it .... lol
Too bad whities and lakers closed yesterday

Most lakes are now open around here. Should be lots of opportunities for fishing this weekend. I'll be chasing crappies myself, but might venture over to simcoe for some perch action too.  Its game on. I had the boat out for the second time yesterday!!  S.
